{
  "text": "This work provides a detailed description of the relationship between the sets of global minimizers (called also optimal sets) of the two nonconvex (combinatorial) problems (C k ) and (R β ), given in (2) and (3), respectively. These sets, see (5) and [CITATION_1] , are always nonempty (Lemma 1 and Theorem 2(b)). Our main results are summarized below. The couple (A, d) satisfies H1.",
